# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# IDE and editor files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Git
**/.git/
**/.gitignore

# Node modules (will be installed during build)
**/node_modules/

# Test projects
**/UnitTest/
**/*Test*/
**/*Tests*/

# Documentation
**/*.md
**/docs/

# Docker files (prevent recursive copying)
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore

# Logs and temp files
**/Logs/
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak

# Environment-specific config
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.production.json

# NuGet packages (will be restored during build)
**/packages/

# Legacy/unused projects
**/DataLayer.LINQ/
**/DataLayer.MOQ/
**/DataLayer.NHibernate/
**/AlwaysMoveForward.AnotherBlog.Web.NHibernate/
